{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"41d5e5839037c91b93be37eb930fba2c2daae78e4d7772785979b59be11fe8b2","digest":{"component_or_area":"Jira reconciler creation-channel attribution and legacy inference","key_entities":["creation_channel","creation_channel_inferred","apply_inbound_records.py","inbound_translate.py","_event_meta","_ensure_inbound_assignee_identity","import_ndjson.py","_provenance.py","_processors.py","_project_legacy_creation_channel","process_create","process_snapshot","reducer/_version.py","validate_creation_channel","LEGACY_JIRA_AUTHOR","LEGACY_JIRA_ENV_ID","source_id","source_created_at","source_author","source_env","jira-* ID","test_creation_channel_jira.py","test_creation_channel_import.py","test_export_ndjson.py","test_schema_coverage.py","docs/output-schemas.md"],"problem_keywords":["creation_channel","jira provenance","legacy inference","ndjson import","source provenance","outbound sync non-rewrite","identity creation","channel attribution","heuristic audit metadata","negative controls"],"propositions":["Inbound Jira materialization records validated creation_channel=jira for the new ticket and any placeholder identity created by that path, independent of reconciler author/env overrides.","Binding or pushing an existing cli/mcp/python ticket outbound to Jira must not rewrite its stored or projected creation_channel genesis provenance.","NDJSON import assigns creation_channel=import on the new local record while preserving source_* fields and not copying the exported source channel.","A legacy ticket with no recorded channel is inferred as jira with creation_channel_inferred=true only when jira-* ID, reconciler author, and reconciler env_id all match exactly; any single mismatch yields unknown without the marker.","Legacy inference uses only creation-stable state (ticket_id, author, env_id) and never tags, bindings, source_* fields, comments, or titles.","creation_channel_inferred is documented as heuristic audit metadata, not a security attestation, and the shared legacy constants resolve under isolated spec-loading."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784313984806077001,"uuid":"b0320c3e-d5de-4396-974e-3de382712fc2"}